Class.example:
      An example where the 3rd step of the   MyFunction is a WxeMethodStep.
      
[Serializable]
public class MyFunction: WxeFunction
{
  ...
  // Step2
  void Step3 ()
  {
    // Your execution logic for this method step.
  }
  // Step4
  ...
}

      An example where the 3rd step of the   MyFunction is a WxeMethodStep
      accepting a  as parameter.
      
[Serializable]
public class MyFunction: WxeFunction
{
  ...
  // Step2
  void Step3 (WxeContext context)
  {
    // Your execution logic for this method step.
  }
  // Step4
  ...
}
